subject: Rogers Cup (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: After missing the previous two months with a back injury, Venus Williams lost to Kirsten Flipkens, 0-6, 6-4, 6-2, at the Rogers Cup in Toronto in just under two hours.
